text: Georgi Moskov (born 27 August 1936) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman flyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Haskovo
